messages.text: AGHH THIS IS KILLING ME
Hahah are you still waiting?
YUP
Didn’t your appointment “start” half an hour ago?
this is what I’m SAYING
pure torture
At least your dad’s there
whatever, he’s reading some fishing magazine in a world of his own
Lol
So how is this place?
I don’t know…it’s like every other dentist office waiting room?
it’s near my house…I don’t know...
you know how there’s always the same brochure stacks and posters in every dentist and doctor office?
yeah haha I know what you mean
They have them here, but they’re not the same brochures as everyone else. It’s weird.
One of them says Imperfections on it, and inside is just pictures of teeth. No information.
What do the other ones say?
Uhh Purification. Discovery. History.
Ooh read Purification to me
Haha ok weirdo
Well I would but the pictures inside are identical to the ones in the Imperfections brochure...
and again no words inside
the pictures are exactly the same?
I mean, if they’re different it’s so slight that I can barely tell. What would be the point of that?
no idea
also apparently I’ve been hogging these too long, because the lady at the window is staring at me
She seems to be seething with rage in my general direction…which is cool
Is it busy
uh dude we’re the only ones in here
huh
AND she just “AHEM”ed at me. Ok we’re done with that
lol I’m dying
I hope this is entertaining for you
you have no idea. I just hope it’s entertaining for you
sure i love feeling more than vaguely unsettled at a weird ass dentist office...
adding to the great feeling going to the dentist already has
oh fantastic, well apparently it’s my time.
Stay Tuned for more in the exciting adventures of Nate Helmsworth!
hahah k
15 minutes later
having a blast?
just more sitting in a room with a slightly yellower white wall than the white wall in the waiting room
woohoo
also my dad was walking over with me but then we turned the corner to one of the 16,000 identical rooms...
and he didn’t follow us, so Im just sitting here alone. dick
Guess he couldn’t take the excitement lol
The “lure” of fishing was too powerful
Get it???
sigh
it looks just like how you’d expect. I’m sitting on that white paper on the chair.
You know, that white paper that if you slightly touch it has this huge melodrama
there’s more kewl posters and stuff tho. Want me to snoop while I wait?
ooh Yes plz :)
don’t get caught
meh I’ll just play it off like I was looking for tissues or somethin
omg we just hit the jackpot! There’s a whole book like those brochures!
so jealous of you right nowww…
just more pictures?
actually no this is kinda cool. It’s in this squiggly writing like Arabic.
Usual messed up teeth pics. I have no idea what it says but I gotta say i dig it
there’s a bunch of diagrams. One shows this arrangement of these dots around the dentist chair
Dots?
yeah, don’t know what that’s about. Maybe the dots are these candles in the drawer…
candles? Uhh
they’re like no other candles I’ve ever seen, but that’s what they’ve got to be
sure they’re not some kind of equipment?
5 minutes later
FUCK
lol what
ok so this is going to sound really strange but one of the cabinets wasn’t for supplies...
it was stairs down to like a basement or something
What??? You didn’t go down there
didn’t have the chance, the hygienist came in
you think she saw you looking?
nah
would that matter?
think you can trust her? Dude what if she saw??
probably didnt…anyway, it’s time for the delightful cleaning. Goin under DA CLAW. lol to be continued
20 minutes later
that sucked
she said the dentist will be in in a second
well you survived
I’m gonna go look in that cabinet again
NATE! Jesus he could come in any second
Stop it. Nate. Seriously!!!
I’ll be fine. What could happen
10 minutes later
Nate? You ok
ewfijfhg
what?
What??
30 minutes later
hey
oh thank god. What’s happening? Are you done?
cant really say much. hiding
hiding? From what??
the dentist
he came busting in and he was crazy looking.
huge whites around his eyes and this hair that looked like hed been electrocuted.
they dont normally put you under for a routine exam right?
No nate they definitely do NOT
Where are you “hiding”
they were messing with my phone. anyway I’m in the basement
i think
What???
in a ditch, dont think he can see me. i can hear him walking around opening and closing stuff looking for me.
hes huge, his steps make the whole ground around me shake
kara there were these bodies everywhere
they had equipment clamped to their teeth and heads. skeletons. smelled horrible. the candles around them
call 911 for me
what are you gonna do??
just have to stay quiet and hidden. think he’ll give up soon
he keeps calling out my name. says he needs to floss my brain to remove the imperfections
i dont know
5 minutes later
the police should be on their way. Nate???
did they believe you?
sort of
its quiet now, i think he left to look somewhere else
OH fuck hes standing right above me
just hang on a little longer!!
he says he needs to fill the cavity?
Cavity? What? How?
with cement
